{"tid":2147420,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"[佛歌]沉默看經 聽到佛光呼應 繼而平靜到訪這娑婆之境","createTime":"2020-08-09T08:32:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-02T16:20:33.000Z","uid":77642,"like":31,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"5c4104c5e4ee5c4aa48fc1ffb27656ff9260d689","tid":2147420,"uid":77642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T08:32:54.000Z","msg":"好耐無寫佛歌，今日送大家：娑婆之境<br />\n同大家一齊探索下和尚家既寂寞<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n娑婆之境(原曲：一人之境)<br />\n<br />\n剎塔裡凝望 眾道笑臉八個十個<br />\n法相裡搖盪 拜佛中感寂寞<br />\n撒去了回望 有著丁點孤寡 像佛陀<br />\n想看穿三世的妄 望透天清氣朗<br />\n<br />\n蕞林內邊走邊想想法印 竟發現滿身亂塵<br />\n觀想內心 亂了袈裟髮鬢 念記釋迦教訓<br />\n<br />\n一個人原來都早有佛性 諸覺菩提全部都得証<br />\n沉默看經 聽到佛光呼應<br />\n繼而平靜到訪這娑婆之境<br />\n如來也很高興 獨個俯瞰每顆山幽之嶺<br />\n開光了的聖水 取出剃刀 剃度懶說明 no~<br />\n佛祖心裏做證<br />\n<br />\n無明欲起悲歡阻擋悟覺 心智業障中隕落<br />\n無常是空願去貪嗔去惡 佛法中找正確<br />\n<br />\n一個人原來都早有佛性 諸覺菩提全部都得証<br />\n沉默看經 聽到佛光呼應<br />\n繼而平靜到訪這金剛界之境<br />\n如來也很高興 獨個觀看世間變幻事情<br />\n開光了的聖水 釋出泡影 聽著那阿含經<br />\n佛光心裹回應<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有興趣可以重溫番我改既另一首佛歌：<br />\n無盡佛法：<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/641701/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/641701/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"04a749de47912d07cebd69c3c7c6da11e7be2e11","tid":2147420,"uid":183576,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T08:51:28.000Z","msg":"我佛你"},{"pid":"00f2b6d94f5a51fdab5300d26efc4a26a7a25642","tid":2147420,"uid":183576,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T09:08:54.000Z","msg":"想G連登有冇可能再出到新老衲大碟"},{"pid":"01ff89e9115e31f34d3704442b004b0b9406391d","tid":2147420,"uid":104096,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T03:32:56.000Z","msg":"支持，推"},{"pid":"be50853117d8cf69bd82e8dc09cb98622900f16b","tid":2147420,"uid":77642,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T03:34:11.000Z","msg":"點解咁都有負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bce328296bb3a8832d23e15d371bf86ebac4bb2","tid":2147420,"uid":77642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01ff89e9115e31f34d3704442b004b0b9406391d","tid":2147420,"uid":104096,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T03:32:56.000Z","msg":"支持，推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T03:34:29.000Z","msg":"多謝支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc24809aaee365824d85792aee4e0d8078f9e4d4","tid":2147420,"uid":154406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T07:41:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji